notification.demoDataNotFound: No Demo Data found. Please install any RH-Webdesign Theme with Demo Data to continue.
notification.demoDataHint: In some Cases Demo Data will add a CMS Page to your main Category - if you are installing Demo Data in Live System, please do not forget to remove/hide the Demo CMS Page. Please also make sure that you replace the supplied images, because some of them are copyrighted.
